Title: Snuff
Plot: Catherine is called in by a pornographic-film developer to view graphic footage from a snuff movie. Grissom investigates when a body, smothered with fire ants, is found stuffed inside a large toolbox.
GuestStars: Tyler Christopher, William Mapother, Niecy Nash, Sal Lopez, Stephen Spacek, Larry Clarke, Meredith Giangrande, Blair Williamson, Sam Hennings
